name: Air France 777-328ER [F-GZNO] Heavy Landing at Toronto Pearson ᴴᴰ
description:
With a spotting stop at Pearson on my way back to Calgary, I can finally say that I've spotted at all four busiest airports in Canada (YYZ, YVR, YUL, YYC). Here we have AF356 making a, shall we say, interesting arrival on runway 23 at Toronto-Pearson International Airport. I've got a couple more interesting YYZ videos coming up, so stay tuned! Enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
